            "title": "Understanding GDP: Why Imports Don't Actually Reduce Economic Growth",
            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Panoramic view urban cityscape singapore with investment theme background\" data-id=\"951792690\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/951792690/image_951792690.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">primeimages</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The role of imports in GDP - Gross Domestic Product - confuses many people. The current political discussion about tariffs has triggered some of the misunderstanding. This article aims to help business leaders understand what this critical economic indicator means, and the role that policy</p>",
